result.name: Queen's Cafe (Festival Walk)

reviews.text:
Of all the branches, this one serves the best food. Best borscht soup in town. I had their beer  battered fish and chips which is quite tasty. 

There is however no service with a smile, their servers were quite arrogant and snobbish ruining the overall  dinning experience. Prices are moderately high.
Local food, I like the retro style with quality food
Food are well prepared and match the price. Friendly staff and great atmosphere
Delicious Borscht and yummy steak, good service.

Used to come here for great afternoon tea, but really disappointed this time. Tldr: gross food at a fairly high price.

Have just had lunch here with 3 others: 2x fish with pasta lunch set, 1x club sandwiches and 1x ox tongue with corn and rice.

Portion size: large.

Quality: they use Lurpak spread with the bread which is nice. But that's basically the only good thing. 

Pasta was not great- think the menu said angel hair but it wasn't.

Ox tongue was really salty, a bit stringy and though fairly tender not tender enough for ox tongue nor for my grandma to eat. It was smothered in a cheap creamed corn that had little flavour and the rice tasted/felt undercooked/old.

Club sandwiches were horrendous: the toasted bread was good but the flavour combo was weird- chicken and ham meat slices with gross (artificially thickened?) mayo and lettuce, roast beef with gherkins, then fried egg with tomato layers. Really weird. Not sure if there are rules to a club sandwiches but I've never seen that combo before and now that I have, I wouldn't recommend it.

Cleanliness: good.

Service: ok, but not good for what this place is trying to achieve. 

Price: between 100-200 per meal.

result.adr_address: 香港九龍塘達之路80號又一城L1-18
result.formatted_address: 香港九龍塘達之路80號又一城L1-18
result.name: 皇后飯店 (又ㄧ城)

reviews.text: 環境👍🏻 服務👌🏻
等位成日都要等好耐，落單又慢，真係廢到一個點
路經又一城想起有呢間西餐廳，就叫咗個午餐。好懷念英式餐廳嘅環境，全港都所餘冇幾。價位中上，平均一個午餐連加一佰一元左右，服務態度好，上菜時間適當，環境舒適。但午餐時間最好12:30 前入座，如果唔係就要排隊啦。

Of all the branches, this one serves the best food. Best borscht soup in town. I had their beer  battered fish and chips which is quite tasty. 

There is however no service with a smile, their servers were quite arrogant and snobbish ruining the overall  dinning experience. Prices are moderately high.

皇后飯店由又一城開到而家一直咁多年，睇返價錢其實同以前無太大分別，對比起其他餐廳，加價叫唔多，而環境夠靜，同朋友靜靜地傾計其實係好好既選擇！

同朋友每人叫左一個晚餐，賣相好好，食物質素亦好高，服務員既態度都好好，會留意你主動嚟幫你，佢見我同朋友打算自拍，仲埋嚟主動話幫手影相，到停左又有主動問需唔需要熱返熱之類，件牛會唔會太生等等，服務員服務態度的確係少見的。

裝修方面保留住過往格調，有老店舊西餐感覺，但好新既，應該一直有翻新過，要一提既係佢地個湯好足料，羅宋湯係勁多餸好杰的，飲落口唔太味精，而個麵包除左熱之外亦係脆邊，呢點好驚喜！

仲有就係件鵝肝煎得好香好脆，絕對係搶晒成件牛，成為今晚既主角！呢間餐廳喺呢個商場真係我最愛

result.name: Festival Walk

reviews.text: Good arcade to shop for medium to medium-high end brands in a spacious environment with both restaurants and food court to suit varying tastes of customers. Great parking lot. Multiple sakes receipts accepted for free parking.

Very crowded and very clean like a hospital. Come here on Sunday and you can enjoy waiting for a table for an hour with everyone. Best place if you want to buy a Rolex for $900,000 to go with your yacht sitting in a port in Italy.
Multiple restaurants and shops. A very big mall, and a nice theater to watch movies. The restaurants were also very nice. A very good shopping mall overall.

I like Festival Walk as it is rarely super crowded like the malls at Sha Tin always seem to be. The TASTE supermarket is fantastic here with a range of products from around the world including Waitrose products and a good frozen section. Other stores I like here are Zara Home, Log On, M&S and the Cinema which let's you bring Starbucks in. I sometimes come here to walk around on rainy days too as it is so big and there are very few shoppers with suitcases.

I like Windows shopping here.cause if not people mountain people sea. Can very relaxed to take a look.some shop I used take a look.like hk a female designer. She design Chinese match west.she control color very. Very good. Also one best of world shoe shop. Tecstoni.name may be not correct. It is one of best Italian designer band shoe shop.
